Mrs. Hudson, there is a woman in my sitting room!

286
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,450
是你故意安排的吗
Is it intentional?

287
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:39,920
她是客户 我说你出去了 但她坚持要等你回来
She's a client. Said you were out, insisted on waiting.

288
00:08:40,970 --> 00:08:43,660
您愿意坐下吗
Would you, er, care to sit down?

289
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,840
您问她来做什么了吗
Didn't you ask her what she wanted?

290
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,390
你自己问她啊
You ask her!

291
