00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:24,330
您抱着和解的希望
You have come to this agency as a last resort,

309
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,900
万不得已来到这里
in the hope that reconciliation may still be possible.

310
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,540
我的天啊 福尔摩斯
Good Lord, Holmes!

