except wander around taking notes, looking surprised?!

328
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:12,660
够了
Enough!

329
00:10:14,710 --> 00:10:17,670
舞台已经备好 帷幕已经升起
The stage is set, the curtain rises.

330
00:10:18,810 --> 00:10:20,180
我们要准备开始演出了
We are ready to begin.

331
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:22,520
开始什么演出
Begin what?

332
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:26,750
有时若想查明一桩案子 另一桩必先水落石出
Sometimes to solve a case, one must first solve another.

333
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:31,290
- 你又接新案子了吗 - 是一桩很古老的旧案
- Oh, you have a case, then, a new one? - An old one, very old.

334
00:10:32,430 --> 00:10:33,730
我必须深入调查
I shall have to go deep.

335
00:10:34,260 --> 00:10:35,260
深入调查什么
Deep? Into what?

336
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,310
自身
Myself.

