1055
00:53:19,940 --> 00:53:22,940
纯粹的理性被情节剧推翻了
Pure reason toppled by sheer melodrama.

1056
00:53:22,940 --> 00:53:24,650
一句话概括你的人生
Your life in a nutshell.

1057
