1066
00:54:02,400 --> 00:54:05,310
所有的事情 我们会需要一张清单
Everything. We will need a list.

1067
00:54:10,520 --> 00:54:12,850
好孩子
Good boy.

1068
00:54:12,850 --> 00:54:15,850
不 我还没有完成清单
No, I haven't finished yet.

1069
00:54:15,850 --> 00:54:19,020
莫里亚蒂恕不同意
Moriarty may beg to differ.

1070
00:54:20,730 --> 00:54:24,100
他想要我分心 要我脱离正轨
He's trying to distract me. To derail me.

1071
00:54:24,100 --> 00:54:25,680
是的
Yes.

1072
00:54:25,690 --> 00:54:28,100
他是镜头上的裂缝 软膏里的苍蝇
He's the crack in the lens, the fly in the ointment,

1073
