Press are having a ruddy field day.

1083
00:55:53,000 --> 00:55:55,130
到现在还有记者在外面等着
There's still reporters outside.

1084
00:55:55,150 --> 00:55:57,590
他们一直都在那里 我没法摆脱他们
Oh, they've been there all the time, I can't get rid of them.

1085
00:55:57,590 --> 00:56:00,890
我一直都在忙着给他们泡茶呢
I've been rushed off my feet making tea.

1086
00:56:00,910 --> 00:56:02,720
你为什么要给他们泡茶
Why do you make them tea?

1087
00:56:04,210 --> 00:56:06,470
我不知道 我就是这样做了
I dunno, I just sort of do.

1088
00:56:08,050 --> 00:56:11,210
