Which is strange, because he likes that bit.

1091
00:56:14,750 --> 00:56:17,460
他还说这案子简单到 我都能解决了
Said it was so simple I could solve it.

1092
00:56:17,460 --> 00:56:19,250
他肯定只是夸张而已
I'm sure he was exaggerating.

1093
00:56:22,710 --> 00:56:24,710
你觉得他这是在干什么呢
What's he doing, do you think?

1094
00:56:24,710 --> 00:56:27,290
- 他说他在等 - 等什么
- He says he's waiting. - For what?

1095
00:56:27,290 --> 00:56:31,080
等恶魔 我不觉得这有什么奇怪
The devil. I wouldn't be surprised.

1096
00:56:31,080 --> 00:56:32,960
什么样的人都来过这里
We get all sorts here.

1097
00:56:34,750 --> 00:56:39,330
- 有消息就给我发电报 - 好
- Well, wire me if there's any change. - Yeah.

1098
00:57:21,950 --> 00:57:25,000
我要说的话 你都已经知道了吧
Everything I have to say has already crossed your mind.

1099
00:57:25,200 --> 00:57:27,910
那我的答案 你也都知道了吧
Then possibly my answer has crossed yours.

1100
00:57:28,680 --> 00:57:30,100
像子弹般穿过
Like a bullet.

1101
00:57:37,320 --> 00:57:38,530
手拿睡袍里
It's a dangerous habit,

1102
