to finger loaded firearms in the pocket of one's dressing gown.

1103
00:57:44,050 --> 00:57:46,070
还是说你很高兴看到我
Or are you just pleased to see me?

1104
00:57:51,240 --> 00:57:53,010
你一定不会介意 我做些预防措施
You'll forgive me for taking precautions.

1105
00:57:53,010 --> 00:57:54,320
如果你没做防御措施 我才介意呢
I'd be offended if you didn't.

1106
00:57:54,330 --> 00:57:58,160
很显然 我也礼尚往来了
Obviously, I've returned the courtesy.

1107
00:58:06,820 --> 00:58:11,660
我喜欢你的房间 闻起来非常得
I like your rooms. They smell so...

1108
00:58:13,910 --> 00:58:15,170
有男子气概
manly.

1109
00:58:15,990 --> 00:58:18,900
你肯定在此之前就来过这里了
I'm sure you acquainted yourself with them before now.

1110
00:58:18,910 --> 00:58:20,500
你总是不在家
Well, you are always away,

1111
00:58:20,510 --> 00:58:23,030
总在为"斯特兰德杂志"出去冒险
on your little adventures for The Strand.

1112
00:58:23,030 --> 00:58:25,950
告诉我 插画师也跟你一起出去旅行吗
Tell me, does the illustrator travel with you?

1113
00:58:25,950 --> 00:58:29,580
你推理的时候 还要摆姿势吗
Do you have to pose... during your deductions?

1114
00:58:29,610 --> 00:58:32,530
我不在的时候 你来过我公寓六次了
I'm aware of all six occasions you have visited these apartments

1115
00:58:32,530 --> 00:58:34,400
- 我都注意到了 - 我知道
- during my absence. - I know you are.

1116
00:58:36,670 --> 00:58:40,170
顺便说一句 你的床真是很舒服啊
By the way, you have a surprisingly comfortable bed.

1117
00:58:44,470 --> 00:58:47,480
你知道灰尘大部分 是人体皮屑组成的吗
Did you know that dust is largely composed of human skin?

1118
00:58:47,650 --> 00:58:49,490
我知道
Yes.

1119
00:58:50,700 --> 00:58:53,490
不过尝起来不太一样 人的皮肤还是更新鲜些
Doesn't taste the same, though, you want your skin fresh.

1120
00:58:53,490 --> 00:58:56,120
- 这个有点太脆了 - 你不坐下吗
- Just a little crispy. - Won't you sit down?

1121
00:58:56,120 --> 00:58:58,490
人就是这样 你知道吧
That's all people really are, you know,

1122
00:58:58,490 --> 00:59:00,280
都是随风飘散的灰尘
dust waiting to be distributed.

1123
00:59:00,280 --> 00:59:02,070
而且飘得到处都是
And it gets everywhere. Ugh.

1124
00:59:02,070 --> 00:59:05,030
存在于每一口呼吸里 在每一缕阳光里起舞的
In every breath you take, dancing in every sunbeam,

1125
00:59:05,030 --> 00:59:07,450
都是精疲力竭的人啊
all the used-up people.

1126
00:59:07,450 --> 00:59:09,560
真有意思 你还是坐下...
Fascinating, I'm sure. Won't you sit...

1127
00:59:09,580 --> 00:59:13,040
人啊 无法保持一尘不染
People, people, people! Can't keep anything shiny.

1128
00:59:15,410 --> 00:59:16,910
你介意我开枪吗
Do you mind if I fire this?

1129
00:59:17,770 --> 00:59:19,690
就清理一下灰尘而已
Just to clean it out.

1130
00:59:36,810 --> 00:59:38,480
就是这样 还是别玩了
Exactly, let's stop playing.

1131
00:59:38,480 --> 00:59:40,350
我们不需要用玩具来杀掉对方
We don't need toys to kill each other.

1132
00:59:40,350 --> 00:59:42,790
- 那样就不亲密了 - 坐下
- Where's the intimacy in that? - Sit down.

1133
00:59:42,810 --> 00:59:45,080
- 为什么 你想知道什么 - 是你选择过来的
- Why? What do you want? - You chose to come here.

1134
00:59:45,120 --> 00:59:46,940
不对 你知道这个答案是错误的
Not true, you know that's not true.

1135
00:59:47,760 --> 00:59:50,220
你想知道什么 夏洛克
What do you want, Sherlock?

1136
00:59:50,770 --> 00:59:52,270
真相
The truth.

1137
00:59:53,040 --> 00:59:56,050
那个啊 真相很无聊的
That. Truth's boring!

1138
00:59:59,470 --> 01:00:00,740
你没想到我会
You didn't expect me to

1139
01:00:00,740 --> 01:00:03,130
出现在犯罪现场 对吧
turn up at the scene of the crime, did you?

1140
01:00:03,340 --> 01:00:06,760
可怜的尤斯塔斯先生 他罪有应得
Poor old Sir Eustace. He got what was coming to him.

1141
01:00:06,860 --> 01:00:08,480
但不可能是你杀了他
But you couldn't have killed him.

1142
01:00:08,480 --> 01:00:12,190
那又怎么样 这很重要吗 真是够了
Oh, so what? Does it matter? Stop it. Stop this.

1143
01:00:12,190 --> 01:00:13,440
你根本不在乎尤斯塔斯先生
You don't care about Sir Eustace,

1144
01:00:13,440 --> 01:00:15,020
或是那个新娘 或是其他东西
or the Bride, or any of it.

1145
01:00:15,020 --> 01:00:16,340
这整个案件中只有一件事
There's only one thing in

1146
01:00:16,340 --> 01:00:18,770
你觉得有意思
this whole business that you find interesting.

1147
01:00:18,770 --> 01:00:21,310
我知道你在干什么
I know what you're doing.

1148
01:00:23,440 --> 01:00:24,260
新娘把枪放进了嘴里
The Bride put a gun in

1149
01:00:24,260 --> 01:00:25,860
